#env
#LESS STARTUP OPTIONS
# -R ANSI COLOR ESCAPE SEQUENCE ARE OUTPUT IN RAW FORM
# -S DO NOT WRAP LINES
# -N SHOW LINE NUMBERS
# -J DISPLAY A STATUS COLUMN AT THE LEFT EDGE OF THE SCREEN.
# -i IGNORE CASE BUT IF A PATTERN CONTAINS UPPERCASE LETTERS, THEN THAT SEARCH DOES NOT IGNORE CASE
# -M LONG PROMPT
# -F quit if one screen
# -X Without it -F option leave no file contents ( this disable termcap initialization and deinitialization strings to the terminal.)
